### 健康检查
GET http://localhost:8080/ping

### Gateway 路由到 order-service
GET http://localhost:8080/orders/ping

### 查看商品
GET http://localhost:8080/catalog/merchants/10/skus

### 将商户产能调为 1，便于演示排队
POST http://localhost:8080/queue/merchants/10/limit
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "limit": 1
}

### 第一个订单：直接成单并占用产能
POST http://localhost:8080/orders/submit
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-Id: 101

{
  "requestId": "demo-submit-101",
  "merchantId": 10,
  "addressId": 20,
  "items": [
    { "skuId": 1, "quantity": 1 }
  ],
  "remark": "少辣"
}

### 第二个订单：商户满载，返回 QUEUED
POST http://localhost:8080/orders/submit
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-Id: 102

{
  "requestId": "demo-submit-102",
  "merchantId": 10,
  "addressId": 21,
  "items": [
    { "skuId": 2, "quantity": 1 }
  ],
  "remark": "不要葱"
}

### 查询订单列表，拿到 payOrderId、orderId、ticketId
GET http://localhost:8080/orders

### 模拟支付第一个订单
POST http://localhost:8080/payments/10001/mock-pay

### 通知 order-service 支付成功，推进订单状态并确认库存和券
POST http://localhost:8080/orders/10001/pay-success

### 商户接单，不释放产能
POST http://localhost:8080/fulfillment/orders/10001/accept
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "requestId": "demo-accept-10001"
}

### 出餐完成，释放产能并自动推进等待票据成单
POST http://localhost:8080/fulfillment/orders/10001/meal-ready
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "requestId": "demo-meal-ready-10001"
}

### 查看 ticket 已变为 ORDER_CREATED，且新增了排队转订单
GET http://localhost:8080/orders

### 查看排队服务状态
GET http://localhost:8080/queue/internal/tickets

### 秒杀领券
POST http://localhost:8080/vouchers/1000/seckill
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-Id: 201

{
  "requestId": "demo-claim-201"
}

### 查看券包
GET http://localhost:8080/vouchers/wallet
X-User-Id: 201
